OL,3,CExecutive urged to produce anti-
OL,4,Cpoverty strategy
OL,6,FA new campaign group has formed,
OL,7,Furging the Executive to produce a
OL,8,Fstrategy to tackle poverty in Northern
OL,9,FIreland.
OL,11,FThe latest figures show 349,000 people
OL,12,Fare living in poverty here, which is
OL,13,Falmost one in five of the population.
OL,15,FThe Anti-Poverty Strategy Group, which
OL,16,Fis made up of almost 20 charities and
OL,17,Fcivil society organisations, is
OL,18,Fcalling on ministers to publish a
OL,19,Fstrategy as a matter of urgency.
