OL,6,F"This work is more urgent today than
OL,7,Fever before," said Trasa Canavan from
OL,8,FBarnardo's NI, Chair of the Anti-
OL,9,FPoverty Strategy Group.
OL,11,F"In Barnardo's NI, we deliver over 45
OL,12,Fdifferent services throughout Northern
OL,13,FIreland, and we see the impact of
OL,14,Fpoverty in every service."
