OL,3,CExecutive urged to produce anti-
OL,4,Cpoverty strategy
OL,6,FKellie Turtle from Age NI, who is also
OL,7,Fpart of the group, said: "Age NI is
OL,8,Fpleased to be a part of the Anti-
OL,9,FPoverty Strategy Group as we are
OL,10,Fdeeply concerned about the toll
OL,11,Fpoverty is taking on older people,
OL,12,Fthousands of whom phone our advice
OL,13,Fservice for help every year.
OL,15,F"We want to see an Anti-Poverty
OL,16,FStrategy that can help to eradicate
OL,17,Fpoverty at every stage of life with no
OL,18,Ffurther delay from the Northern
OL,19,FIreland Executive."
