OL,3,CExecutive urged to produce anti-
OL,4,Cpoverty strategy
OL,6,FIn a statement, the Department for
OL,7,FCommunities said: "The Northern
OL,8,FIreland Executive Anti-poverty
OL,9,FStrategy is at the final stages of
OL,10,Fdevelopment and it is anticipated that
OL,11,Fit will be presented to the Executive
OL,12,Fin the coming weeks.
OL,14,F"The strategy aims to mitigate
OL,15,Fimpacts, reduce the risk of falling
OL,16,Finto poverty and support people in
OL,17,Fexiting poverty through long-term,
OL,18,Fjoined-up working across departments."
